Package: visorfuego
Title: Quarto Leaflet Viewer for Fire Risk and Active Fires
Version: 0.5.37
Authors@R: person("Santiago", "Mota", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Static Quarto dashboard for AEMET GeoTIFF fire risk maps, NASA FIRMS active fire detections, EFFIS/Copernicus WMS layers, GISCO/NUTS operational summaries, automatic FIRMS cluster alerts and historical trend tracking and Web Mercator-aligned AEMET overlays and valid-date handling for AEMET classic forecasts, and robust EFFIS static rendering from WMS GetMap with GetCapabilities TIME discovery, multi-server fallback and WMS 1.1.1/1.3.0 probing, plus GDAL-based EFFIS TIFF-to-PNG conversion fallback.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends:
    R (>= 4.2)
